quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  48,16,"Maakan tultu…ďe …ďen e yim…ďe ladde …ďeen: "Arma nde noddete…óon e yim…ďe joomiraa…ďe doole tii…óu…ďe. Ho…ďon …ďe maa…óum …ďe silma. Si on …óoftike, Allah okkat on mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īundi; si on nduŇčtii ii no huccitirno…óon oya tuma, O leptira lepte mu'usuu…óe"."
  48,17,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e hoore …ďum…óo on, wonaa e la∆īoowo on wonaa kadi e nawnu…óon bakkaatu fawii. Kala …óoftii…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, O naadoyay mo Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mum. Kala kadi …óuurnii…óo, O leptiray mo lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  48,18,"GooŇč…óii Allah welano gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, tuma …ďe ahondiraynoo e maa…óa ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, O jippini dee∆īere nden e ma…ď…ďe, O warjorii…ďe uddital …ďadiingal,"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi …ďe ke…ď…ďitotoo. Allah siforii won'de pool…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi ke…ď…ďito…óon, O yaccinani on ndii …óoo, o suri juu…óe yim…ďe …ďeen e mo'on, fii yo wonu Ma'ande wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, O fewnira on laawol Pocciingol."
  48,21,"E wo…óndi goo ndi on ha…ótanaali taho, Allah kan no hu…ďindii ndi. Allah siforii won'de ka…ótan…óo kala hu'unde."
  48,22,"Hay si yeddu…ďe …ďeen ha…ďiino on, …ďe huccintinayno …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe …óen, refti …ďe ke…ďataano gi…óo wonaa ballao."
  48,23,"∆äuum ko sunna Alla pe∆ī∆īunoo…óo ko adii. A he…ďantaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu."